<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>MoviePass</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-neutral-900 text-white text-center">
    <header class="py-6 px-12 bg-neutral-700">
      <nav class="flex justify-center md:justify-end items-center">
        <ul class="flex">
          <li class="mr-2"><a href="/login" class="p-2">Log In</a></li>
          <li><a href="/signup" class="p-2">Sign Up</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <h1 class="text-teal-400 text-5xl mt-6 md:mt-12">MoviePass</h1>
    <p>
      Create movie lists (and share them with your friends... when I get around
      to adding the functionality)
    </p>

    <section
      class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center mt-12 px-6 md:px-0"
    >
      <p class="text-lg underline">Features to add:</p>
      <ul class="text-left list-disc max-w-lg">
        <li>(Currently) Styling site with TailwindCSS</li>
        <li>Update homepage and login/logout pages -- add more information</li>
        <li>Give user feedback when adding to/removing from list</li>
        <li>Create shareable lists</li>
        <li>Possibly add TV Shows and Anime lists</li>
        <li>Community lists (Upvote based?)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-lg mt-6 underline">Changelog:</h2>

      <h4 class="my-4">09/06/2022</h4>
      <ul class="text-left list-disc max-w-lg">
        <li>Began styling site with TailwindCSS</li>
        <li>
          Change "Add to List" button to "Remove from List" if movie exists in
          your list
        </li>
        <li>Update site name</li>
      </ul>

      <h4 class="my-4">09/02/2022</h4>
      <ul class="text-left list-disc max-w-lg">
        <li>
          Migrated from
          <a href="https://www.omdbapi.com/">OMDb API</a> to
          <a href="https://www.themoviedb.org/">TMDB API</a>
          for movies information database
        </li>
        <li>Return multiple movies instead of just one</li>
        <li>Add check if movie does not exist</li>
        <li>Add temporary, simple styling</li>
        <li>
          Began migration to
          <a href="https://www.themoviedb.org/">TMDB API</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <footer class="py-6 px-12 mt-12 w-full bg-neutral-700">
      <h3>Created by <a href="https://kylerriggs.com">Kyler Riggs</a></h3>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
